---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Kenneth Frencher">
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">About Me</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Innovative Software Engineer with over 15 years of experience in full-cycle software development 
          and technology solutions. Co-Founder of Trivium Software Inc., where I lead the development of 
          cutting-edge applications, specializing in ServiceNow and web technologies.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I have always had a passion for technology. From building computers to crafting software solutions. 
          I can adapt to whatever technology stack that is being used and learn quickly.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Over the years I've been part of many projects. Some I have built completely on my own, and others 
          have been larger efforts with teams. I love a challenging project that allows me to push the limits 
          of what I know.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-gray-900">Professional Journey</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-6 mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Co-Founder, Trivium Software Inc.</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Leading the development of enterprise applications with a focus on ServiceNow platform solutions, 
            web technologies, and full-stack development. Driving innovation in software architecture and 
            team leadership.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-gray-900">Core Competencies</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Programming Languages</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
              <li>JavaScript (ES6+)</li>
              <li>Python</li>
              <li>Java</li>
              <li>Groovy</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Frameworks & Libraries</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
              <li>AngularJS</li>
              <li>Google Polymer</li>
              <li>ExtJS</li>
              <li>jQuery</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Platforms</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
              <li>ServiceNow</li>
              <li>Spring Framework</li>
              <li>JEE (Java Enterprise Edition)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Methodologies</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
              <li>Full-stack Development</li>
              <li>Agile (Scrum)</li>
              <li>Unit Testing</li>
              <li>Automated Functional Testing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg mt-12">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 italic">
            "For projects and code samples feel free to explore my GitHub. I'm always open to discussing 
            challenging projects and new opportunities to push the boundaries of technology."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
